Package edu.colorado.cires.cmg.awszarr

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    S3ClientWrapper
    A wrapper around the S3Client from the AWS SDK v2.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AwsS3ClientWrapper
    A S3ClientWrapper that uses a S3Client to access files from an S3 bucket.
    AwsS3ClientWrapper.Builder
    Builds a new AwsS3ClientWrapper.
    AwsS3ZarrStore
    An implementation of a Store that is backed by an AWS S3 bucket
    AwsS3ZarrStore.Builder
    Builds a new AwsS3ZarrStore
    FileMockS3ClientWrapper
    A mock implementation of a S3ClientWrapper that is backed by the local filesystem.
    FileMockS3ClientWrapper.Builder
    Builds a new FileMockS3ClientWrapper
